data.name: label14.Text
data.value:
The amount of gallons of water per shower is detemined by two things:
1. Shower head flow rate 2. Amount of time spent showering
The shower head flow rate can be determined by knowing the gallons of water per minute (GPM) each shower head uses. The average GPM most shower head uses is 2.5 gpm. I have provided 3 main GPM's in my calculator that shower heads fall in. The GPM can be multiplied by the amount of time you spend showering to determine how much gallons of water you are using per shower.

data.name: txtThirdParagraph.Text
data.value: I encourage you to help us battle this global problem and take action by viewing the tabs up above. Clean-ups have been a successful way of helping protect our environment but did you know taking shorter showers can also help as well? Learn more about it by clicking the shower calculator tab above! Any donation whether it be big or small can make an impact as well!

data.name: txtSecondParagraph.Text
data.value: Water for Everyone is an application designed to battle this global problem and help reinforce global goal 6: Clean Water and Sanitation. We believe that clean water should be accessible to everyone and with your actions, we can create an impact and help save many lives. Our goal is to provide you with ways to help this situation that is causing problems for people around the world and even around us.

data.name: txtFirstParagraph.Text
data.value: Did you know that more than 2 billion people are living with the risk of reduced access to freshwater resources? By 2050, at least one in four people is likely to live in a country affected by continuous shortages of fresh water. It is apparent that this has devastated the lives of many and will continue to if no action is taken.

data.name: label17.Text
data.value: Clean-ups have been a big part of helping our environment stay healthy. There are many clean-ups around the world involving big organizations like Worlds Oceans Day and 4ocean. The best part is, clean-ups can be in all sizes whether you want to participate in a big clean-up event or schedule your on event. Consider particpating for a clean-up event and help protect our world! Click the button to sign up now or create your own event!
